[Auction "S"]
1NT pass 2H pass 2S pass 2NT pass 4S pass pass pass
[Result ""]
{NORTH has an invitational (9 point) hand with five ♠s.

She bids it in the standard way - first transfer SOUTH to ♠s, then invite

the game by bidding 2NT.

SOUTH, with 17 points and three ♠s, accepts the game invitation and chooses 4♠.}
